      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle is in honest, poor condition and definitely shows its age with significant cosmetic and mechanical wear, but it\u2019s a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or someone looking for a fixer-upper at a great price! It's ready for some TLC to get back into shape.",
