      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade asset in pristine condition, both mechanically and aesthetically. Every surface reflects a meticulous commitment to preservation, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery state. We invite discerning buyers to inspect this masterfully curated vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    }
